      <title>受胡塞武装袭击的货轮船员因火灾弃船</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-15/houthi-stricken-cargo-carrier-s-crew-abandons-ship-due-to-fire</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国军方称，周六，一艘散货船遭胡塞导弹袭击，船员因无法控制船上火势而弃船逃生。]]></description>
