    <item>
      <title>最新民意调查显示英国保守党将在选举中惨败</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-15/latest-polls-show-uk-conservatives-headed-for-election-wipeout</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据周日报纸公布的三项新民意调查显示，英国首相里希·苏纳克领导的保守党将在 7 月 4 日的大选中遭遇历史性惨败。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-15/latest-polls-show-uk-conservatives-headed-for-election-wipeout</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 15 Jun 2024 20:25:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>李克强开始澳大利亚之行，象征意义掩盖紧张局势</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-15/china-s-li-begins-australia-trip-with-symbolism-masking-tensions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国国务院总理李强开始对澳大利亚进行访问，这是自 2017 年以来中国高层领导人首次访问澳大利亚，标志着在亚太地区安全紧张局势升级的背景下两国关系得到改善。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-15/china-s-li-begins-australia-trip-with-symbolism-masking-tensions</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 15 Jun 2024 19:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
